+## Class: IpcMainSharedWorker
+
+> Communicate asynchronously from the main process to a shared worker.
+
+Process: [Main](../glossary.md#main-process)
+
+This API is a variation of [`IpcMain`](ipc-main.md) targeted for communicating
+with one shared worker.
+
+### Instance Methods
+
+#### `ipcMainSharedWorker.on(channel, listener)`
+
+* `channel` string
+* `listener` Function
+  * `event` [IpcMainSharedWorkerEvent][ipc-main-shared-worker-event]
+  * `...args` any[]
+
+Listens to `channel`, when a new message arrives `listener` would be called with
+`listener(event, args...)`.
+
+#### `ipcMainSharedWorker.off(channel, listener)`
