+* `listener` Function
+  * `event` [IpcMainEvent](structures/ipc-main-event.md) | [IpcMainDedicatedWorkerEvent](structures/ipc-main-dedicated-worker-event.md)
+  * `...args` any[]
+
+Alias for `ipcMainWebContents.on`.
+
+#### `ipcMainWebContents.removeListener(channel, listener)`
+
+* `channel` string
+* `listener` Function
+  * `event` [IpcMainEvent](structures/ipc-main-event.md) | [IpcMainDedicatedWorkerEvent](structures/ipc-main-dedicated-worker-event.md)
